Upgrade eClient
Option 1: Upgrade eClient from 8.4.02 to 8.4.03
Software:
 IBM II4C new version; (Bob will provide)
 EClient application package(the .ear file) the customized SIA version not the original eClient. (Bob
will provide)
Steps:
1) Backup the :
livingstonCustom.properties
IDM.properties
IDMadminDefaults.properties
From:
D:\Program
Files\IBM\WebSphere\AppServer\profiles\AppSrv01\installedApps\vQ9BeClientNode01Cell\
eClient_WF.ear\eclient.war
2) You need to uninstall eClient ear file from websphere administration
Connect to : http://localhost:9060/ibm/console/unsecureLogon.jsp as admin and uninstall it
from here :
Or uninstall it from Control Panel Programs and Features.
3) Uninstall the II4C
4) Install the new version for II4C
5) Install the new eClient 8.4.3
6) upgrade SIA eClient 8.4.3. from websphere administration
7) Copy the
livingstonCustom.properties
IDM.properties
IDMadminDefaults.properties
from the backup directory to the new location of eclient.
